    ],
    chronologyEn: [
      'Surpanakha propositions Rama then Lakshmana, is rebuffed, and loses her nose and ears.',
      'Khara and Dushana attack on Surpanakha\'s behalf and are killed by Rama; Surpanakha flees to Ravana.',
